sequenceDiagram
participant U as 用户
participant T as Tokenizer
participant E as Embedding
participant TF as Transformer
participant S as 采样器
participant Out as 输出
U->>T: "解释什么是 RAG"
T-->>E: [token_1, token_2, ..., token_n]
E->>TF: 向量序列
loop 多层 Transformer
TF->>TF: Self-attention + 前馈网络
end
TF-->>S: 概率分布
S->>S: 采样策略
S-->>Out: 下一个 token
Out->>E: 拼回上下文继续
Note over E,TF: 循环直到<br/>结束或达到最大长度
Out-->>U: "RAG 是检索增强生成..."
